overview: The later teenage years can be a troubling time for a young woman. All sorts of strange and exciting urges might make a girl act just a little... nuts. Fortunately, legendary superstud Rocco Siffredi offers his special style of hands-on counseling. "Rocco's Psycho Teens 2" stars seven luscious teenage beauties doing things no sane girl would admit to!
title: Rocco's Psycho Teens 2
